  "insert a -> arrow with <C-l>
    inoremap <C-l> ->

  "insert a => hash rocket <C-k>
    inoremap <C-k> =><Space>

  "insert an erb <% %> tag (with no output) using <C-e>
    inoremap <C-e> <%<space>%><left><left><left> 
    "TODO: make a command that will surrounded the highlighted text in
